Dear Stakeholders,

I hope this message finds you well. We would like to inform you of an upcoming planned maintenance activity for our Zabbix production instance. This maintenance is essential to ensure the continued reliability and performance of our monitoring system.

Maintenance Details:

Date and Time: From 21st October 2023, 10:30 PM CST, to 22nd October 2023, 5:30 AM CST.
Duration: Approximately 7 hours.
During this maintenance period, our Zabbix instance will be temporarily inaccessible. We understand that this may cause some inconvenience, and we apologize for any disruption this may cause to your operations.

Once the maintenance activity is completed, you will regain full access to the Zabbix system. Our team will work diligently to ensure that the downtime is kept to a minimum, and we will strive to finish the maintenance ahead of schedule if possible.

We appreciate your understanding and support as we work to maintain the high standards of performance and security of our systems. If you have any questions or concerns about this maintenance activity, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.

Thank you for your cooperation, and we apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.

Best regards
